  right:-40%-->hume right -40% isliye diya taki woh chup jaye right side me.-40% isliye diya kyuki width 40% le rakha hai humne.
               aur hum agar right -40% kar rahe hai toh ye overflow kar dega x direction me. Iska solution hai
               hum body me overflow-x:hideen laga denge
  
